  "description": {
    "zh": "好吧，我想你老是做同一件事也挺无聊的，换点花样如何呢。\n我想看看你用霰弹枪的能力，试着干掉一些人，我不在乎你干的是谁，Scav、Raider、PMC，都行。\n\n学习如何使用这种武器很重要。真有意思，这种武器在发明了一个多世纪后仍然如此令人厌恶却又危险。\n\n无论如何，在你杀戮的同时，我还希望你能找到一些霰弹枪，哪怕它们状况不佳，只要主要部件完好，我有个朋友能把它们改成很酷的样子。\n\n也许有一天你会见到她。总之，祝你好运。",
    "en": "Alright fine, enough of this place, some variety can't hurt after all.\nI wanna see how good you are with shotguns, shoot up some guys, I don't care who, bandits, locals, PMCs, whatever.\n\nAlways important to learn how to use these kinds of weapons, interesting to see how these guns are still so hated and dangerous after over a century, truly fascinating.\nAnyway, while you are on your killing spree, I want you to find some shotguns yourself, and it doesn't matter how broken they are as long as the main parts are intact, I have a friend who can turn them into something cool.\n\nMaybe you'll meet her one day. Anyway good luck out there."
  },
